1.0.name: wordpress/diggz-et
1.0.description:
What this plugin does:

Automatically displays a "digg" button for each post and page.

Features:

  • Full admin options available for digg buttons.

  • Choose between auto created JavaScript buttons or custom CSS buttons (API mode)

  • Display digg buttons at the top left, top right or bottom of the post/page.

  • Manual button placement with shortcode See Faq.

  • Can hide buttons on home page, pages, posts, tag pages, archives and search results page.

  • Hide buttons on a single page or post See Faq.

  • Media Scan Feature - Use multiple types of media with digg See Faq.

  • digg threshold option with API mode

Features Planned or in Development:

    <
